Paula Jones.

45:03.559 --> 45:05.762
Could she help me?

45:05.896 --> 45:07.764
Help you with what?

45:07.898 --> 45:09.465
Dating
within your own bloodline?

45:11.134 --> 45:15.271
Her lawyers are calling
character witnesses on Clinton.

45:15.405 --> 45:18.341
If they make me testify,
this whole thing becomes public.

45:18.474 --> 45:19.776
I love it.

45:19.910 --> 45:21.277
I'll make a few phone calls.

45:21.411 --> 45:23.279
Monica can never find out.

45:23.413 --> 45:25.415
Okay, dear.

45:27.583 --> 45:29.585
(phone ringing)

45:32.355 --> 45:34.891
Lucianne Goldberg,
as I live and breathe.

45:35.025 --> 45:36.526
-To what do I owe this honor?
-(copier beeps)

45:37.760 --> 45:40.263
Are you sitting down?

45:42.765 --> 45:44.801
RICHARD:
You're not going to believe
what I just heard.

45:44.935 --> 45:47.904
There's an intern
in the Casa Blanca

45:48.038 --> 45:51.741
who indulges a certain lothario
with oral sex in the pantry.

45:51.875 --> 45:53.810
There's a real witness
who will testify to it.

45:53.944 --> 45:56.479
-You're kidding.
-(laughing): I kid you not.

45:56.612 --> 45:57.981
What's her name?

45:58.114 --> 45:59.482
Linda Tripp's the name
of the witness.

45:59.615 --> 46:01.651
No, no, no.
What's the intern's name?

46:01.784 --> 46:05.388
Lewisky.
Monica Lewisky.

46:05.521 --> 46:08.324
-You have the number
to the Jones lawyers?
-Yeah.

46:08.458 --> 46:09.625
(beep)

46:11.127 --> 46:13.196
(line ringing)

46:17.467 --> 46:19.469
(typing)

46:34.650 --> 46:36.819
(sighs)

46:41.657 --> 46:44.260
-Mr. Bacon?
-Ms. Lewinsky.

46:44.394 --> 46:46.429
(sighs)
I'm here to inform you that, um,

46:46.562 --> 46:48.698
as of January 1st,
I will no longer be available

46:48.831 --> 46:50.600
to work
for the Department of Defense.

46:50.733 --> 46:52.702
So the day has come.

46:52.835 --> 46:54.704
I'm moving to New York City.

46:54.837 --> 46:57.207
Well, we'll be sad
to lose you, Monica.

46:57.340 --> 46:59.575
What are you going to be doing
in the Big Apple?

47:01.511 --> 47:04.347
Um, I'm going to move on
with my life.

47:34.210 --> 47:36.212
*

47:51.394 --> 47:53.663
(doorbell rings)

47:56.066 --> 47:58.234
(sighs)

48:07.910 --> 48:10.346
Are you Ms. Linda Tripp?

48:10.480 --> 48:12.115
Uh-huh.

48:12.248 --> 48:14.017
This subpoena requires you
to testify

48:14.150 --> 48:17.253
as a witness
in Jones v. Clinton.

48:22.825 --> 48:24.894
-(knock at door)
-(door opens)

48:25.028 --> 48:28.231
Mr. President, the Jones team
faxed over the witness list.

48:28.364 --> 48:30.233
You have a moment to go over it?

48:30.366 --> 48:32.969
-Sure.
-Most of the names are what

48:33.103 --> 48:35.638
we anticipated--
Willey, Flowers.

48:35.771 --> 48:39.442
The only one that didn't sound
familiar was Monica Lewinsky.

48:41.544 --> 48:44.214
I looked into it.
She was a White House intern.

48:44.347 --> 48:46.616
Does that name sound familiar?

48:48.551 --> 48:50.153
Because even if there's
a small chance

48:50.286 --> 48:53.489
that she or any of these women
might pose a problem,

48:53.623 --> 48:55.891
you can tell me.

48:56.026 --> 48:59.329
We can still settle this.

48:59.462 --> 49:01.697
We can make it all go away.

49:04.134 --> 49:06.169
Bob,

49:06.302 --> 49:08.804
do you think I'm fucking crazy?

49:11.407 --> 49:13.409
Mr. President.

49:43.339 --> 49:45.341
